 《铁蝴蝶》演员道格·英格尔去世，享年 78 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-butterflys-doug-ingle-has-died-age-78-3759577?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=iron-butterflys-doug-ingle-has-died- 78岁Alex RigottiSun, 26 May 2024 19:43:26 +0000 Music NewsNews..PsychedeliaRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3759577 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="道格·英格尔（Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images 拍摄）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，经典迷幻摇滚乐队的创始成员于 5 月 24 日“在家人在场的情况下”去世</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-butterflys-doug-ingle-has-died-aged-78-3759577">《Iron Butterfly》的 Doug Ingle 去世，享年 78 岁的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="道格·英格尔（Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images 拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>经典迷幻摇滚乐队 Iron Butterfly 的创始人、主唱兼管风琴手道格·英格尔 (Doug Ingle) 去世，享年 78 岁。他是该乐队经典阵容中最后一位幸存成员。</p><p>在网上分享的<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/stlouisclassicrock/permalink/7804841212929183/">Facebook 帖子</a>中，英格尔的儿子小道格·英格尔 (Doug Ingle Jr) 分享道：“我怀着沉重的心情和巨大的悲伤宣布我父亲道格·英格尔的去世。爸爸今天晚上（5 月 24 日）在家人的陪伴下平静地去世了。</p><p> “谢谢爸爸，你是一位父亲、老师和朋友。珍惜的爱的回忆我将带着我余下的日子在这段人生的旅程中继续前行。爱你的爸爸。”</p><p>铁蝴蝶歌手的死因尚未公布。 </p><figure id="attachment_3759578" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3759578" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3759578" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024.jpg" alt="道格·英格尔（Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images 拍摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Doug-Ingle-singer-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3759578" class="wp-caption-text">道格·英格尔（Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p> Iron Butterfly 于 1966 年由 Ingle、鼓手 Jack Pinney、贝斯手 Greg Willis 和吉他手 Danny Weis 在加利福尼亚州圣地亚哥组建。然而，乐队在签署唱片合约后因其阵容而闻名，其中包括英格尔、鼓手罗恩·布希、贝斯手李·多曼和吉他手埃里克·布莱恩。布莱恩于 2003 年去世，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/various-artists-2688-1248571">多尔曼于 2012 年去世</a>，布什最近 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-butterfly-drummer-ron-bushy-has-died-age-79-3032698">于 2021 年去世。</a></p><p>该乐队因 1986 年由 Ingle 共同创作的热门歌曲“In-A-Gadda-Da-Vida”而闻名。这首歌被认为是硬摇滚和重金属音乐的鼻祖之一。</p><p>英格尔继续创作了其他经典作品，如《灵魂体验》、《我们的生活》和《逍遥骑士》。最终，乐队于 1971 年解散，尽管 Ingle 偶尔会随乐队巡演，最近一次是在 1999 年。</p><p> 2014 年有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/various-artists-1121-1211368">乐队正在用 Ingle 的歌曲《Ingle Jr》创作一张新专辑</a>。吉他手迈克·皮涅拉（Mike Pinera）当时告诉<em>经典摇滚</em>：“我们刚刚与一些原始成员一起重组了铁蝴蝶乐队……乐队的原始鼓手兼创始人罗恩·布希（Ron Bushy），以及我自己和小道格·英格尔（Doug Ingle Jr.）。”这张专辑从未实现。 </p><p><iframe title="IRON BUTTERFLY - IN A GADDA DA VIDA - 1968（原版完整版）CD 声音和 3D 视频" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UIVe-rZBcm4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iron-butterflys-doug-ingle-has-died-aged-78-3759577">《Iron Butterfly》的 Doug Ingle 去世，享年 78 岁的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
